languages.text: [draft]Any enemy of the Psyker that is either {g|Encyclopedia:PushGlossary}pushed{/g} away or fall {g|Encyclopedia:ProneEffect}prone{/g} suffers {g|Encyclopedia:PsyRating}<u>psy rating</u>{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:IrreducibleDamage}irreducible damage{/g}. The same happens to enemies that either push or knock prone one of the Psyker's allies.

traits.locale_text: [draft]Any enemy of the Psyker that is either pushed away or become prone suffers <u>psy rating</u> irreducible damage. The same happens to enemies that either push or make prone one of the Psyker's allies.
